WEBVTT

1
00:05:02.590 --> 00:05:04.300 
天哪
Dear God.

2
00:05:04.420 --> 00:05:05.880 
怎么了
What?

3
00:05:06.010 --> 00:05:08.300 
这个信号居然是
The signal turned out to be --

4
00:05:08.430 --> 00:05:10.260 
没有其他说法来描述它了
there's no other way to put it --

5
00:05:10.390 --> 00:05:12.090 
- 指南 - 什么东西的
-Instructions. -For?

6
00:05:12.220 --> 00:05:15.140 
飞行器 先生 一台穿越星际的飞行器
A vehicle, sir, an interstellar vehicle.

7
00:05:15.270 --> 00:05:17.880 
我们需要一个飞行员 不知道有没有志愿者
We'll need a pilot. I wonder if there's a volunteer.

8
00:05:18.980 --> 00:05:22.190 
图表上明确表示需要一个身材矮小的副驾驶
Oh, the schematics specify a second, smaller pilot.

9
00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:24.310 
我是说 这方面写得真的很明确
I mean, they really specify smaller.

10
00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:26.780 
必须正好是1米6
They have to be exactly 5'3”.

11
00:05:26.910 --> 00:05:29.360 
Chang 虽然你主修的是文科
Chang, you may have majored in Liberal Arts,

12
00:05:29.490 --> 00:05:31.780 
但是你将要创造历史了
but I think you're about to make history.

